  "slug": "true-doors",
  "title": "True Doors",
  "description": "Makes the doors more real and looks so cool while in the third_person.",
  "body": "<p align=\"center\">True Doors replaces the flat vanilla door item textures with proper models so doors look natural when held in your hand.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/73218ad9ce76576ec367888dcccc43d3fb8a3af8.png\" alt=\"True Doors Title\" width=\"900\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\">Every door uses a custom item model, making them appear correctly shaped instead of a flat rectangle in the inventory.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b2a7e39a7694ee97d8c3d1c53bc55f530b48dccd.png\" alt=\"Horizontal Line\" width=\"1000\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/87d148459e70c92d2402db4ad93323d2fee1094d.png\" alt=\"Sample\" width=\"200\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c59db29af91870b12f6431956eae7484d032eef5.png\" alt=\"Items\" width=\"400\"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/63334d4b92428643fa28713d48716175b04a93b9_0.webp\" alt=\"Holding\" width=\"400\"></a></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b2a7e39a7694ee97d8c3d1c53bc55f530b48dccd.png\" alt=\"Horizontal Line\" width=\"1000\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/083972eb6a2d7a64c2d34d5b7accfeebe09dc4c4.png\" alt=\"Supported Mods\" width=\"450\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\">This resource pack specifically supports Not Enough Animations mod and First-person Model mods.</p>\n<p align=\"center\">Many other mods are also affected automatically.</p>\n<details><summary>Not Enough Animations mod:</summary>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c9d208eadf94222b3c74f9607ce55af90291f3db.gif\" alt=\"Not Enough Animations Mod\" width=\"450\"></p></details>\n<details><summary>First-person Model mod:</summary>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b08cd77a68e6317a3c2b9575a3424f57262ce345_0.webp\" alt=\"First Person Mod\" width=\"450\"></p></details>\n<details><summary>Hold My Items mod:</summary>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/0dd6e62c3ffa23a97fd8b2a565e02ad53ae491f1_0.webp\" alt=\"Hold My Items Mod\" width=\"450\"></p></details>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b2a7e39a7694ee97d8c3d1c53bc55f530b48dccd.png\" alt=\"Horizontal Line\" width=\"1000\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img \nsrc=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/ad6912b13f922fd1812626b29b21a831f2cc3b8f.png\" alt=\"Update\" width=\"200\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\">This update improves the accuracy and polish of the pack.</p>\n<p align=\"center\">Door edge textures (top, bottom, left, and right) now use proper textures instead of stretched pixels.</p>\n<details><summary>Update 1.1:</summary>\n<b>Door edges now use proper textures.</b> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <b>\"Broken or incompatible\" warnings have been fixed.</b></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/f9a6585fae7b6e238309876c35931d8691d58330.png\" alt=\"Before and After\" width=\"200\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/2a24739355bbddffaea1f3f14b1f73d9b6e64d6f.png\" alt=\"Warning\" width=\"400\"></p><p align=\"center\">\n<b align=\"center\">The pack icon has been updated.</b>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/70337f36e9bbe9c9ef8df67745a00af1bc2cca19_0.webp\" alt=\"Profile Change\" width=\"500\"></p></details>\n<p align=\"center\">The pack icon has been updated and the resource pack \"Broken or incompatible\" warnings in Minecraft have been fixed.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b2a7e39a7694ee97d8c3d1c53bc55f530b48dccd.png\" alt=\"Horizontal Line\" width=\"1000\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/true-doors\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/9d3cd7c29b765ea051a12413a8580e6b002c04ff.png\" alt=\"Modrinth Download Button\" width=\"300\"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/true-doors\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/425e2c3a8f7ca6ba05b2d4ea767640abc7b5ae71.png\" alt=\"CurseForge Download Button\" width=\"300\"></a></p>",
